{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ENTER AN OLD SCHOOL STEALTH EXPERIENCE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Carry out your objectives in sandbox missions. Use your preferred playstyle, knocking out enemies and hiding their bodies, climbing out of reach, or resorting to head-on combat. Use gadgets to make your way through the dilapidated environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A faction called the scarves is clamoring lands. Your home town is the last bastion of its continent still standing to fight them. The town's main defense lies it's pneumatic weapons, and your crew has been sent across seas to find a working compressor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/extras/5topics.jpg?t=1734027167\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The current Early Access version has about 4 hours of content in 3 missions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">old school stealth experience with little hand holding with indicators</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A story centered around survival and connivery, with dialog that conforms to player's actions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Post-apocalyptic environments with a moody atmosphere fortified by the sound track</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies with lightness-based vision</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">3 options for a non-lethal takedown</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gadgets like boats, doze grenades and a grappling hook that help you make your way through the missions</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734027167","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1715390/page.bg.jpg?t=1734027167","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c